HEADWORD: Bib
<hw>Bib</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To drink; to sip; to
tipple.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He was constantly <qex>bibbing</qex>.</q>
